additional_data.description: The spirit of a chest used to gather items in anticipation of married life. She's so powerful that she can lift her wooden chest weighing many times more than herself with a single hand. She's also a bit hoarder, gathering things left and right and cramming them into her beloved chest. She'll put anything in there —literally ANYTHING— and people are starting to wonder when it's going to get full. But she doesn't seem to harbor any such concerns. Let's just say her chest contains many secrets...
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Romance of the Demon and Sword" Event: Defeat LVL 10, 20, 30 Noddy.
◦ "Romance of the Demon and Sword" Event: Random drops after LVL 10.
◦ "Romance of the Demon and Sword" Get a First and Second Half Ranking of 6001~10000.
◦ "Romance of the Demon and Sword" Get a Total Ranking of 7501~10000.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slightly increases total Event Points gained during the "Romance of the Demon and Sword" event.
